<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:13:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美联储政策决定前美元接近五个月高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-01/</link><description>美元兑一篮子货币小幅升至今年最高水平，周三美国股指期货在美联储政策决定之前下跌，但由于许多欧洲和亚洲市场休市，交投清淡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 08:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>壳牌退出中国电力市场业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-exits-china-power-market-businesses-2024-05-01/</link><description>壳牌周三表示，作为首席执行官 Wael Sawan 致力于专注于利润更高的业务的一部分，壳牌已退出中国电力市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 08:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-exits-china-power-market-businesses-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>华为备受瞩目的消费者首席执行官余承东转变角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-high-profile-consumer-boss-richard-yu-shifts-role-2024-05-01/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国华为技术有限公司 (HWT.UL) 已将备受瞩目的消费者业务负责人余承东调任该部门董事长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 06:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-high-profile-consumer-boss-richard-yu-shifts-role-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国启动下一代航母海试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-launches-sea-trials-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-05-01/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国周三为第三艘也是最先进的航母福建舰进行了海试。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-launches-sea-trials-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国海警加剧南海紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</link><description>一名官员表示，在北京使用水炮造成两艘船只受损后，菲律宾周三指责中国海警加剧南海紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾对中国就职后的演习保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</link><description>台湾最高安全官员周三表示，在当选总统赖清德本月就职后，台湾对中国进行军事演习保持警惕，并补充说中国已经开始使用不寻常的新策略。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:34:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国和中国主要市场需求降温，星巴克下调年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</link><description>星巴克周二下调了年度销售预期，此前该公司报告同店销售额近三年来首次下降，原因是该公司面临美国和中国这两个最大市场的咖啡需求疲软的困境。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国劳工官员呼吁企业退出中国新疆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-labor-official-calls-companies-exit-chinas-xinjiang-2024-04-30/</link><description>美国劳工部官员周二表示，出于对强迫劳动的担忧，国际公司无法在新疆负责任地运营，应该离开中国西部地区。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-labor-official-calls-companies-exit-chinas-xinjiang-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>石墨矿商游说美国政府对中国采购的电动汽车材料征税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/graphite-miners-lobby-us-govt-impose-levy-china-sourced-ev-material-2024-04-30/</link><description>北美石墨矿商正在游说美国政府对来自中国的三种石墨产品征收 25% 的关税，以对抗北京对汽车电池关键材料的垄断。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/graphite-miners-lobby-us-govt-impose-levy-china-sourced-ev-material-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>被关押在国外的美国人的家人需要更多帮助和信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/families-americans-held-abroad-want-more-help-information-2024-04-30/</link><description>尽管拜登政府最近安排了囚犯交换，但仍有美国人的家人在外国被拘留，他们在周二恳求至少提供有关亲人的更多信息，同时等待并希望他们获释。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 16:41:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/families-americans-held-abroad-want-more-help-information-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行在出人意料的首席执行官搜寻中必须优先考虑亚洲专业知识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-must-prioritise-asian-expertise-surprise-ceo-search-2024-04-30/</link><description>在首席执行官诺埃尔·奎恩 (Noel Quinn) 的领导下，汇丰银行应对了全球疫情，并在反叛投资者的推动下分拆了这家拥有 160 年历史的银行。投资者表示，他的意外离职是加速其战略重心转向亚洲的一个机会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-must-prioritise-asian-expertise-surprise-ceo-search-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>拜登签署新备忘录以加强美国关键基础设施的安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-signs-new-memo-boost-security-us-critical-infrastructure-2024-04-30/</link><description>总统乔·拜登周二签署了一份新的国家安全备忘录，以提高美国关键基础设施的弹性，取代已有十年之久的政策。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-signs-new-memo-boost-security-us-critical-infrastructure-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大推迟2023年年度业绩；股票继续停牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-delay-2023-annual-results-2024-04-30/</link><description>中国恒大集团表示将推迟公布年度业绩，因为其清算人需要时间来“确定这家陷入困境的房地产开发商的现状”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:38:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-delay-2023-annual-results-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯顿·马丁寻求对阿隆索在中国冲刺赛的处罚进行审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/aston-martin-seek-review-alonsos-china-sprint-penalty-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二，英国车队阿斯顿·马丁和法拉利就费尔南多·阿隆索在中国大奖赛冲刺赛的处罚寻求“审查权”，一级方程式赛会干事召集阿斯顿·马丁和法拉利参加听证会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 13:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/aston-martin-seek-review-alonsos-china-sprint-penalty-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>主要买家中国的铜冶炼厂对必和必拓与英美资源集团的合作持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/copper-smelters-leading-buyer-china-wary-bhp-anglo-american-tie-up-2024-04-30/</link><description>作为全球最大的矿产铜买家，中国冶炼厂担心，如果当地被称为“大矿商”的必和必拓集团成功收购竞争对手英美资源集团，他们将失去谈判价格的权力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 13:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/copper-smelters-leading-buyer-china-wary-bhp-anglo-american-tie-up-2024-04-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>